title: Coronavirus Break
description:
Lala and Randall want everyone to be well and stay safe during this time of social distancing due to coronavirus! That's what they're doing as Randall tries to get back home to LA from Puerto Rico. The podcast will return with new episodes in the near future!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
